    "description": "在<strong><i>《Age of Wonders 4: Eldritch Realms》</i></strong>扩展包中征服幽影深渊的深处。以魔能君主恐吓您的敌人，使用强大的新魔典，在改变世界的全球事件中幸存下来，并在黑暗席卷全域之前带领你的人民对抗黑暗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新的地图层：</h2><strong>暗影深渊</strong>。一个充斥着腐败与恐惧黑暗领域，意图侵吞凡人王国。其中包括新的战术战斗地图、十几个可供探索与开发的独特地点，以及暗影恶魔盘踞的新独立派系——<strong>暗影居所</strong>。这些深渊生物是致力于毁灭光明及入侵王国的腐败生物。深渊会对进入其中的单位造成伤害，但是可通过从暗影居所购买<strong>暗影血肉次级转化</strong>来获得豁免。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/9f85fe6fe8482050640afe38b4bf6e84.poster.avif?t=1718726472\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/9f85fe6fe8482050640afe38b4bf6e84.webm?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/9f85fe6fe8482050640afe38b4bf6e84.mp4?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新的统治者类型：</h2>有着恐怖力量的远古存在——魔能君主，已被暗影深渊腐蚀，并拥有独特的<strong>奴役法术施放</strong>机制。选择你作为魔能君主统治者的道路，在支配敌人、操控尸体或狂野的混乱魔法之间做出抉择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/e34f51068eec52d6d1eacc81db64c8d9.poster.avif?t=1718726472\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/e34f51068eec52d6d1eacc81db64c8d9.webm?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/e34f51068eec52d6d1eacc81db64c8d9.mp4?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 个新的故事世界：</h2>返回阿斯拉，并在一场决定世界命运的史诗级冲突中捍卫它。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 种新的形态：</h2>● 赛伦形态 <br>● 昆虫形态<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 种新的坐骑：</h2>● 标准甲虫坐骑<br>● 异域死亡甲虫坐骑<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/b6dc21bbd184b436d6b4ecff796692fb.poster.avif?t=1718726472\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/b6dc21bbd184b436d6b4ecff796692fb.webm?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/b6dc21bbd184b436d6b4ecff796692fb.mp4?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >宇宙事件系统：</h2>这类全新的全球事件旨在带来惊心刺激、不可预测的效果。其中包含 4 个名为“丧钟之季节”的小型危机事件，且有着独特的战术地图、单位和机制。完成这些事件可赋予你将自己的英雄变成各自灾祸的能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/b4bb202ea7586a3b4081c12b8a371895.poster.avif?t=1718726472\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/b4bb202ea7586a3b4081c12b8a371895.webm?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/b4bb202ea7586a3b4081c12b8a371895.mp4?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新的魔典：</h2>●<strong> 触手魔典：</strong>擅长使用触手固定和伤害敌人。赋予以触手作为手臂的独特种族单位“收束者”。<br>● <strong>净化之焰魔典：</strong>以光明之力反击深渊黑暗的魔典！在战斗中召唤净化之焰，在保护信徒的同时焚烧异端。<br>● <strong>腐败魔典：</strong>借力打力。将增益转化为减益效果，或者窃取对方的增益为己所用。创造敌方单位的邪恶影像，并将自己的单位转化成暗影行者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/578fd465b26368c1e2629e0ecdfd23cf.poster.avif?t=1718726472\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/578fd465b26368c1e2629e0ecdfd23cf.webm?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401860/extras/578fd465b26368c1e2629e0ecdfd23cf.mp4?t=1718726472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >5 个新的预设统治者</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 个新的领域模板</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 个新的领域特质</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新的界面皮肤</h2>将阴暗的触手伸向了用户界面<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >由作曲家 Michiel van den Bos 创作的 6 首新的音乐曲目</h2>",
